Despite the widespread availability of voice assistants in vehicles, their adoption remains limited. Hubble Abona Flash Itangaje Hagati ya Galagisi  Mugihe ikirere nijoro gishobora kugaragara gituje (kandi ni cyiza cyane), isanzure yuzuyemo ibisasu biturika kandi bigongana. Mubidakunze kubaho muribi bihe byinzibacyuho harimo ibyo bita Luminous Byihuta Ubururu Optical (LFBOTs), bimurika cyane mumucyo wubururu kandi bigashira nyuma yiminsi mike. Ibi bintu byinzibacyuho bigaragazwa gusa na telesikopi ikomeza gukurikirana ikirere. Hifashishijwe icyuma cyitwa Hubble Space Telescope, itsinda mpuzamahanga ry’abahanga mu bumenyi bw’inyenyeri baherutse kureba LFBOT iri hagati yinjeje ebyiri, ahantu ha nyuma bari biteze ko bazabona imwe.  Iri tsinda ryari riyobowe n’umuhanga mu bumenyi bw’inyenyeri Ashley Chrimes, Umushakashatsi w’ikigo cy’ibihugu by’Uburayi gishinzwe ubushakashatsi, wahoze mu kigo cy’imibare y’imibare n’ubumenyi bw’ibinyabuzima (IMAPP) muri kaminuza ya Radboud. Yifatanije na bagenzi be bo muri IMAPP, Ikigo cya 3SRON cyo mu Buholandi gishinzwe ubushakashatsi ku kirere, Cosmic Dawn Centre (DAWN), Ikigo cya Niels Bohr, Ikigo cya Gravitational Wave Astronomie, Observatoire ya Afurika y'Epfo, hamwe na kaminuza nyinshi n'ibigo by'ubushakashatsi. Urupapuro rusobanura ibyo babonye ruzashyirwa ahagaragara mu kwezi kwa buri kwezi kwa Royal Astronomical Society.  LFBOT yambere yagaragaye muri 2018 (AT2018cow) na Asteroid-Terrestrial-impact-Last Alert Sisitemu (ATLAS). Ibi birori byiswe 'Inka,' byari byiza cyane inshuro 10-100 kurenza supernova isanzwe kandi byabereye muri galaxy hafi miriyoni 200 zumucyo (miriyoni 60 parsec). Kuva icyo gihe, abahanga mu bumenyi bw'ikirere bavumbuye LFBOT ku gipimo kingana n'umwaka ku mwaka, bityo bake gusa ni bo bazwi, kandi ni bike cyane bizwi kuri bo. Mugihe inyigisho nyinshi zerekeye impamvu zishobora kubaho zibaho, Hubble aherutse kuvumbura yatumye iki kintu kirushaho kuba amayobera.

Ibitekerezo byuyu muhanzi byerekana inyenyeri ebyiri nto ariko zuzuye cyane neutron aho bahurira bagaturika nka kilonova. Inguzanyo: Kaminuza ya Warwick / Mark Garlick  Kugira ngo basobanure ibyo babonye, ​​Chrimes na bagenzi be barimo gutekereza ku bishoboka ko ari ingaruka zatewe no kugongana hagati yinyenyeri ebyiri za neutron zasohowe muri galaxy yabakiriye kandi zari zimaze imyaka miriyari. Ibi bitanga kilonovae, biturika bikomeye inshuro 1.000 kurenza nova isanzwe kandi ni isoko izwi cyane ya Gravitational Waves (GWs). Iyindi nyigisho nuko LFBOTs iterwa no kugongana hagati yinyenyeri za neutron, aho imwe iba magnetar (inyenyeri ya neutron nini cyane).

Perezida Museveni avuga ko yongeye guhohotera muri Isiraheli na Palesitine birababaje.  Perezida Yoweri Museveni wikubye kabiri nk'umuyobozi mukuru w'ingabo, yavuze ko ihohoterwa ryongeye kugaragara muri Isiraheli na Palesitine ribabaje.  Ikinyamakuru The Guardian cyatangaje amasaha ashize, cyemeza urupfu rw'Abisiraheli makumyabiri na babiri mu gihe cy'imvururu zongeye.  Iyi ngingo yavuze kandi ko abantu 545 basigaye bakomeretse, abapfuye bakaba bashobora kwiyongera nyuma y’ibitero byo mu kirere no ku butaka.  Mu gitekerezo cyashyizwe kuri X ku wa gatandatu, Museveni yagize ati: “Ihohoterwa ry’ihohoterwa ryongeye kugaragara muri Isiraheli na Palesitine rirababaje.”  Ati: “Kuki impande zombi zidashyira mu bikorwa igisubizo cy'ibihugu byombi?” aribaza.  Ku bwa Perezida, “kwamaganwa by'umwihariko, ni umuco wo kwibasira abasivili ndetse n'abatari abarwanyi.”

MOSCOW - Perezida w’Uburusiya, Vladimir Putin, yatangaje ku wa kane ko ibice bya grenade yabonetse mu mibiri y’abantu bapfuye bazize impanuka yo muri Kanama y’indege y’umucanshuro w’Uburusiya Yevgeny Prigozhin. Putin yongeyeho ko impuguke zishinzwe iperereza ku mpanuka zasanze nta kimenyetso cyerekana ko indege yagize “ingaruka ziturutse hanze.” Abantu 10 bose bari mu ndege, barimo umuyobozi w'itsinda ry'abacanshuro Wagner, Prigozhin, barapfuye.

Impuguke zemeje ko Vladimir Putin atekereza 'gusohokana n’umuvurungano nka Hitler', aho guhangana n’isuzugura ry’ubutegetsi bw’abaturage be mu gihe afite ubwoba ko yizihije isabukuru ye y'amavuko.  Kreml yari irimo amakimbirane no kutumvikana kuva aho umusirikare mukuru yategetse ingabo ze gutera abaturanyi babo b'amahoro muri Ukraine umwaka ushize. Bake mu bajenerali be bumva neza impamvu abagabo babo bategekwaga mu gihugu, bitwaye ubuzima bw'Abarusiya bagera kuri miliyoni.  Mu ntangiriro z'uyu mwaka Putin yatinyaga ko imperuka yegereje igihe ingabo zo mu itsinda rya Wagner zerekezaga i Moscou mbere yuko ihirikwa ry’ubutegetsi rishobora guhagarikwa. Noneho impuguke ivuga ko abatavuga rumwe n’ubutegetsi nibaramuka bahisemo gukuramo Perezida, yakwiyambura ubuzima nka Adolf Hitler mu 1945 - aho guhura n’agasuzuguro ko kwamburwa ubutegetsi.  Porofeseri Anthony Glees yabwiye izuba ati: “Ashobora kuba arimo kureba pistolet ya zahabu ku meza ye atekereza, yego, igihe kirageze. Niba afite ubwoba buhagije, yego ashobora kugera kuri iyo mbunda. Icyo cyaba igisubizo kandi umuseke mushya uza kuri twe.  Ati: 'Inzira imwe rukumbi icyorezo cya Putin kizadukurwaho, cyane cyane mu mibabaro iteye ubwoba y'abaturage ba Ukraine, ni uko aramutse yiciwe kandi icya kabiri cyiza cyaba ihirikwa ry'ubutegetsi.'  Yongeyeho ko yemera ko umunyagitugu mubi yijihije isabukuru ye y'amavuko - ubwo yujuje imyaka 71 ku ya 7 Ukwakira.  Mu ntangiriro z'uyu mwaka umuyobozi ushinzwe iperereza mu gisirikare cya Ukraine yavuze ko Vladimir Putin “nyawe” amaze umwaka urenga atagaragara mu ruhame. Jenerali-majoro Kyrylo Budanov yikubye kabiri kubyo bavugaga mbere doppelgängers imwe cyangwa nyinshi zikoreshwa mu mwanya wa Putin.  Budanov yavuze ko atazi niba Putin akiri muzima. Mu kiganiro kidasanzwe, Budanov - uyobora ibitero by’indege zitagira abapilote ndetse n’ibikorwa by’ibanga byibasiye Uburusiya - yavuze kuri Putin ati: “Uwo, abantu bose bari bazi, aheruka kuboneka ahagana ku ya 26 Kamena 2022.”

Bya Nora Abdelkrim  Uburusiya bwasabye ko icyemezo cyarwo ku byerekeye amakimbirane ya Palesitine na Isiraheli cyatorwa n’inama y’umuryango w’abibumbye ishinzwe umutekano ku wa mbere Ukwakira, dushobora gusoma kuri konte X (Twitter) y’Umuyobozi wungirije uhoraho w’Uburusiya muri Loni, Dmitry Polyansky. Yabisobanuye agira ati: 'Twakwirakwije mu bagize akanama gashinzwe umutekano mbere yo gusaba aya majwi', akomeza avuga ko Uburusiya bwizeye ko perezida wa Njyanama wa Berezile azemeza aya majwi vuba.  Umwanzuro urasaba ko “imirwano ihagarika ikiremwamuntu ndetse n’ubutabazi butabangamiye.” Iramagana byimazeyo 'urugomo n’imirwano byose byibasira abasivili n’ibikorwa byose by’iterabwoba', tutiriwe tuvuga Hamas mu izina, bitandukanye n’umuhamagaro, mu minsi yashize, Leta zunze ubumwe z’Amerika mu kanama gashinzwe umutekano, 'twamagane byimazeyo iterabwoba ribi. ibikorwa by'umutwe wa kisilamu wa Palesitine. ”  Inkunga kuri iki cyemezo cyubutabazi irakinguye abanyamuryango bose. “Ntukumve ko umushigikiye! Dukeneye ubutumwa busobanutse ku mpande z’amakimbirane. ” Ambasaderi w'Ubushinwa, Zhang Jun, yagize ati: 'Hariho ubwumvikane bugaragara ku bibazo by'ubutabazi.' Yavuze ko 'yiteguye imbaraga zose zizafasha guhagarika imirwano, no gukuraho.'  Nkuko byari byitezwe, Abanyaburengerazuba bagaragaza ko badashaka, kimwe n'Ubwongereza, ambasaderi Barbara Woodward yagereranije ko 'ku kibazo nk'iki, igihe tumaze kubona irimbuka ry'ubuzima bw'abantu, dukeneye igihe cyo kugisha inama, kugira ngo tugire inama zikomeye.' Minisitiri w’ububanyi n’amahanga wa Berezile, Mauro Vieira, avuga ko Brezil nayo yavuze ko yiteguye “gukomeza gukorana bya hafi n’intumwa zose zigana ku mwanya w’Inama Njyanama”.  Biragaragara ko yitandukanije n’umwanya w’iburengerazuba ku gitero cya Hamas, Vladimir Putin, aganira na Minisitiri w’intebe wa Iraki, Mohammed Chia al-Soudani, ku ya 10 Ukwakira, i Moscou, yashinje Washington ko ibintu byakomeje kwiyongera. Ati: 'Mu byukuri sindi jyenyine ntekereza ko uru ari
